divs: Sighting DetailsWas at a camp ground and was looking up at the stars and saw this orb moving across the sky, I then asked the other 2 people that were there to look at this thing in the sky and tell me what they think,. they too thought it was a ufo. For there was no blinking green or red light that a plane would have.. Also no nose what so ever...
